notes:
Invite your teammates: Go to the "+" button in the top bar and select "Invite."

Why should I invite my teammates?     Asana is built for team collaboration. With Asana, your team can share ideas, updates, and conversations, and coordinate work.
    Now that you have your first project set up, invite a few people to try using Asana with you.

After sending invites, consider hosting an Asana kick-off meeting so your team can learn how they will benefit from using Asana: https://asana.com/guide/team/onboard/asana-kickoff
